<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Optional Questions</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ef4444, #f3f4f6, #4f46e5);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        form {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.75rem;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            min-height: 120px;
            resize: vertical;
        }

        textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #4f46e5;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
        }

        button {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.75rem;
            background: #4f46e5;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: #4338ca;
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            form {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            p,
            label {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }

            textarea,
            button {
                padding: 0.6rem;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <form action="/questions" method="POST">
        <h1>Tell Us About Yourself</h1>
        <p>All questions are optional. Feel free to share as much or as little as you'd like.</p>

        <label for="qualities">Write a quality about yourself that defines you as a person (optional)</label>
        <textarea id="qualities" name="qualities" placeholder="Tell us about your defining qualities..."></textarea>

        <label for="hobbies">What kind of hobbies are you into? (optional)</label>
        <textarea id="hobbies" name="hobbies" placeholder="Share your hobbies and interests..."></textarea>

        <label for="about">Tell us more about yourself (optional)</label>
        <textarea id="about" name="about" placeholder="Share more details about yourself..."></textarea>

        <button type="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>
</body>

</html>